				<div class="entry-content">
					<h4>What is HelperPlace?</h4>
					<p>HelperPlace is a powerful website which allows to connect Employers to the best Domestic Helpers or Drivers in your town. We offer the largest jobs opportunities in Hong Kong, Macau, Singapore, Dubai, Doha, Taipei&#8230; HelperPlace is not a recruitment agency and we never required any fees to Domestic Helpers or Drivers.</p>
					<h4 id="frage1_2">Is it free to create my Helper Profile?</h4>
					<p><strong>HelperPlace DOESN&#8217;T charge any fees to Domestic Employees</strong>. We are happy to offer our services to each profile looking for a job. Our service will allow you to choose your employers based on your expectations (location, skills&#8230;).</p>
					<h4 id="frage1_3">How can I contact Employers?</h4>
					<p>To easily contact employers, you just need to create your profile on HelperPlace. Please carefully fill in your profile (add a picture, your skills, experiences&#8230;) and you will increase your chances to get a job.</p>
					<h4 id="frage2_1">How can I Post a Job?</h4>
					<p>To post a job offer, you just need to <a href="post-a-job/index.html">click here</a>. Please&nbsp;carefully fill in your job ads and you will quickly get the best domestic helper for your family. If you want to freely use our service, you just need to <a href="https://www.facebook.com/helperplace">like our facebook page</a>! HelperPlace is also available with more option (30 days, post 20 job offers,..). If you want to enjoy this additional options, please subscribe to our light plan when you post your first job offer.</p>
					<h4 id="frage2_2">How can I contact a Domestic Helper?</h4>
					<p>To contact or connect with candidates, you need to post a job offer. As soon as your job offer will be activated, you will have the possibility to contact your selected profiles.</p>
					<h4><span style="font-size: 1em;">Why HelperPlace is the best solution for Employers ?</span></h4>
					<p>We offer the largest qualified profiles for Helpers, Drivers, or Part Time job. Just a few hours are enough to get some contacts and start the interview process. We are proud to offer the best profiles close to you.</p>
					<h4 id="frage3_2">How can I update my account?</h4>
					<p>Sign In on HelperPlace and visit My Profiles. You will have the possibility to easily update your Job Offer or your Helper Profile. If you have any issues, don&#8217;t hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
					<h4>What is the&nbsp;money-back guarantee?</h4>
					<p>If you’re not fully satisfied with HelperPlace&nbsp;within 7 days, we’ll refund 100% of your purchase price! First-time buyers only.</p>
					<h4 id="frage3_3">I have a technical problem or support issue I need resolved, who do I email?</h4>
					<p>The best way to get in touch with us is to send an email to our support team. Please carefully describe your problem and we&nbsp;will reply back with&nbsp;a solution!</p>
					<h4 id="frage3_4">Forgot password / Trouble signing in</h4>
					<p>Need help with your password? Go to <a href="my-account-2/index.html">login page</a> on HelperPlace, then click on Lost your Password and Enter the email you use for HelperPlace, and we’ll help you create a new password. Just a few minutes later you will receive an email to activate your new password.</p>
					<h4 id="frage3_5">How can I cancel my account?</h4>
					<p>We are sad but we hope to see you later. To cancel your account, you need to Sign In and go to your profile. Then, you just have to remove your job offer or your Helper profile.</p>
